summary:
A reliable, self motivated and experience Sales and Customer Service Consultant, committed to providing excellent client service with a smile. With a proven track record of seven years. Strong in exceeding goals and increasing sales volumes, Adept in conducting sales calls to effectively convey a message and provide information about a product and service. A results-oriented individual that founds her niche in increasing sales, revenues and developing effective and long lasting client relationships.

A professional team player with the ability to develop high retention strategies and provide the client with the right care and support.
